MYSPACE NOT YOURS!

yea im in one of my weird moods....sry i havent wrote in a while.  nothing really happend... ya know same shyt day in day out.. last nite i went to malverne (dont ask why) and chylled with cosgrove and kenny and then i was on the phone the whole nite with kid anthony from queens.  dont really know him but he seems like a cool kid!  brian finally came home from florida!!! yay so happy. meaning this friday im goin to VS! lol when do i ever not go there...i like live there ( more than i did when i was with him).  theres really nothing more to say...OH i got my blue shirt at work...CWG of CEC!!! lol...peace im out!

~DaNieLLe

well as usual my day starts off with waking up at 6:40 and then passing back out until about 7, finally gettin up and then goin to school for 1st period!!! which is a complete bitch and after this year im done with carey!!! dont get wrong, i have so many memories in those halls and classrooms and i'll never forget but i wanna LEAVE!! after 7 periods of bullshyt its off to dance i go!!! after dance im home and during the week no1 is really around so i sit home!!! except for tonite!! my friend danny who i havent seen in forever stopped by to say hi! well little did i know that when my dad came home he was gonna bugg the fuck out!!! he yelled at me and told danny "get the fuck out of my house!!".  

let me fill u in on danny...hes got a girlfriend and nothing was even goin on! we were just catching up because we havent seen each ( i think i said that already)... well now i know that my dads a complete syco!  

on days like these i sit home and think!!! i like to think, its a cool thing.  lay down put on some tunes and think!! yea well todays thinking consisted of 2 things... 1.  Why do things such as backstabbing friends have to happen? 2.  Why did brian have to go to florida this weekend!!? LOL..  everyone tells me that its cute that we still talk but in the back of my mind i have my doubts.  Going off to college next year is a major step in life.  Im going to meet soo many new people! and when that happens hes not even gonna be a thought in mind (unless we start goin out before i go to college!) you never know what lifes gonna bring along...

This weekend just may suck!!  tomorrow (friday) i dont know WTF is goin on! i dont know if im gonna be forced to go out with my mom, or if im meetin up with dee, ana, michelle and catherine to start prom shyt (whole other paragraph) or chyllen with my biffel jenna<3.. Saturday i have work all day and Sunday too.. Thank god that i have monday off BUT i have dance!!!  grrrr then its right back to school tuesday!

Prom - everything that was said before x-mas break has yet to happen!  it was said that we were goin to start all this shyt right when we came back to school!  yea well nothings been done.  i mean ive done a lot buts its all on my own!  ive looked for buses (theres about 30 of us going together), and today i looked for houses!!! ***ANYONE WHO KNOWS ABOUT RENTALS IN THE HAMPTONS LET ME KNOW ASAP*** 

well thats all i have to say for today...peace, im out...

~DaNieLLe

YEA...happy birthday mike...OMG what an amazing nite. first i go to work and then tom tells me to go home so i go home, change mad fast, run to mikes, get in the car and go to hooters!!!! i had sooo much fun!!! lol. i bought my first hooters shirt!!! OH MAN my hooters hangout...LOL..."When i grow up i wanna marry a hooters girl!" haha!!!! what a nite! peace, im out ~DaNieLLe

holy crap monkies...sry i havent updated in a while but so much has happend! well not so much but the most important thing that i had been waiting for finally happend!!  friday nite i went to VS to chyll with my fucker and we talked.  everything that we both had to say came out.  i love him i honestly do! if it wasnt for him i dont think i would be the person i am today!!! but that was my friday nite....last nite i just chylled at phils with everyone and then came home. oh yea jenna stayed over AGAIN, 2 nites in a row.  she really does live here now.  she should just bring a suitcase over on monday and then go home and get new clothes on sunday!  lol...umm today i worked which wasnt bad...i went in at 2 came home and 5.  chylled with jenna again, called thompson after she left and had another really good conversation!  he wants me to go to florida with him...how cute! ugh...okay well im gonna go....peace, im out!

                                                               ...since you've been gone

~DaNieLLe

oh man, its gonna snow again tomorrow. i really cant take the snow nemore. i want spring to be here like right now! Ugh.  neway, today was another normal freaking day! get up, go to school, come home, take a nap, go to dance, come home and then go to sleep! thats usually how my tuesdays go! now that were back at school things for the first semester are like almost done! that means no more english, no more economics!! NICE...i know im passing both so it really doesnt bother me!  next semester i have government and modern novel...EASY!!!  i wont even be like goin to school.  well i lied i have to go for 2nd, 3rd and 9th!!! thats it! woo-hoo! nice...alright well im freakin tired! too much dance.  peace, im out!

~DaNieLLe

OMG...you just dont understand! school starts again tomorrow!! i cant believe it! vacation went sooo fast! im dreading the fact that i have to get up at 6 tomorrow morning, go and sit in a classroom and be yelled at for not shuting up!!! i mean c'mon everyone is gonna be telling their drunken New Years Stories!! lol...jenna moved out today! it was sad but oh the memories! .:+*the things that werent funny were HILARIOUS and the things that were funny just didnt matter, OMG my moms not here im goin to VS and theres nothing she can do about it! Eminem attacted me in the middle of the night! tricia at my nuts and balls!! my Ct boyfriend!!! lol and many more!*+:. Vacation was amazing!!! Only 36 more school days till the next one!! 

DaNieLLe<3
